text: Katarina Ivanovska (; born 18 August 1988) is a Macedonian model and actress. She began her modeling career in 2004, appearing at Milan Fashion Week after winning the Look Models International model search in Macedonia.Katarina Ivanovska. New York Magazine.Model Mania . Hint Fashion Magazine. October, 2004. In December, 2004, she appeared in a pictorial for Elle magazine and has also appeared in Citizen K, Stiletto and the Italian and Russian Vogue. She has been featured on the covers of Diva and Máxima magazines and in advertisements for D&G; in 2006. She is considered the most successful Macedonian model.Dnevnik newspaper "Најуспешниот топ-модел Катарина Ивановска" In 2010, Ivanovska appeared in Serbian Elle magazine.
